      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Fair-condition vehicle priced accordingly. It shows noticeable cosmetic wear on the exterior and interior, with age-related imperfections and signs of regular use throughout. It\u2019s not a perfect or fully sorted example, but it should still suit a buyer looking for basic, usable transportation at a more affordable price point. Expect some deferred maintenance items and a presentation that is more practical than polished.",
