    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Exceptionally clean mint-condition car that has clearly been cared for at a very high level. It presents beautifully inside and out, feels fresh, sharp, and very well kept, and it\u2019s the kind of example that stands out right away. If you\u2019re looking for a truly top-quality, ready-to-enjoy car, this one is easy to be excited about.",
