    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "$4,200 - Older vehicle in poor overall condition and being sold honestly as-is. It shows significant age, wear, and cosmetic flaws inside and out, and buyers should expect mechanical needs and deferred maintenance. Best suited for someone looking for a project, repair candidate, or possible parts vehicle rather than a clean, ready-to-go daily driver. If you want something inexpensive and understand what a poor-condition older vehicle usually needs, this may be worth a look.",
