    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Honest, affordable transportation with plenty of potential. This vehicle is best suited for a value-focused buyer looking for a practical daily driver, a starter car, or a solid project opportunity. It shows its age and is priced accordingly, but it still offers a chance to get behind the wheel for far less than newer alternatives. A smart buy for someone who appreciates straightforward value.",
      "price": 6450.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of potential? This car is a straightforward budget-friendly option that could suit someone needing basic transport, a first fixer-upper, or a handy project. It\u2019s not pretending to be perfect, but it does offer a solid opportunity for the right buyer who wants something inexpensive and usable without breaking the bank. If you\u2019re practical, handy, or just after a cheap car with some life left in it, this one is well worth a look.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Clean, honest project car with strong old-school character and a solid mechanical feel. It starts, runs, and moves under its own power, with an engine that pulls steadily and a drivetrain that feels fundamentally intact. Cosmetically it shows its age and will need attention, but for the right buyer this is a great budget entry point for a commuter, shop truck, or weekend revival. If you want something inexpensive with usable bones and real potential, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 7900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Cheap entry car with plenty of life for the right buyer. Priced to move fast.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is the kind of car that still turns an ordinary drive into a story. It has a well-worn, honest character that gives it real personality, and for the right buyer, that\u2019s exactly the appeal. Whether you want an inexpensive set of wheels, a hands-on project, or something with a little grit and soul, this car offers a chance to own something with presence without spending big. It\u2019s not pretending to be perfect\u2014it\u2019s the kind of machine for someone who appreciates potential, practicality, and a vehicle with a little edge.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
